      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under ISO 9001-certified QMS with documented validation test suite. Version control and change management procedures in place.",
      "rationale": "The FEA software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) is deployed under a documented quality management system. Software validation records, version control logs, and change management procedures satisfy Gradation 3 requirements for a medium-risk model."
