      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical has been verified against standard NAFEMS benchmark problems for linear and nonlinear structural mechanics. Internal code verification suite covers contact mechanics and large-deformation beam-column interactions relevant to this COU."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
