    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is accepted given regulatory precedent for single-condition ASTM F1717 validation and the medium model risk level. E/uval < 1.96 and relative differences < 10% for all QoI confirm adequate predictive accuracy for the COU. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
